{"tid":796382,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"送層2000萬既樓比女朋友","createTime":"2018-08-27T18:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T07:36:01.000Z","uid":185306,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1ae4109fb74d1a94ae06e79541525c36f0afea","tid":796382,"uid":185306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"曾經問過個女仔一個問題<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果你男朋友送層2000萬既樓比你，你會點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一定唔會要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  受唔起，管理費已經交唔起<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無絲打解釋下呢個女仔既思想係咩一回事？"},{"pid":"4447d86d371c37cee73c9c2016245d17c3391985","tid":796382,"uid":92278,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"扮野<br />\n貪錢<br />\n唔知足"},{"pid":"ed0cc60566f955369bbf52c13d532b659ac38c7e","tid":796382,"uid":21558,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"欲拒還迎<br />\n你直接俾住户證佢，佢仲講得出呢番說話先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd9e8c03fbe97960ea4f92d3f74fc828646b799","tid":796382,"uid":46042,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"通常呢啲女仔知道條仔送得20,000,000嘅樓<br />\n<br />\n會扮唔要<br />\n<br />\n因為可以貪更多"},{"pid":"9a7bda5363c5a530ebcbc473599742436213e5f3","tid":796382,"uid":15309,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:08:48.000Z","msg":"人地送比你 冇理由賣左佢/租出去<br />\n既然係咁即係要自住<br />\n咁就要交管理費果啲<br />\n咁樣好無謂姐<br />\n不如索性唔要 你比2000萬佢好過 <br />\n起碼有得慢慢用"},{"pid":"972dc6ea2487deb1c31eb0b67296caba8e238a02","tid":796382,"uid":128921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T21:08:10.000Z","msg":"即係叫你直接畀二千萬佢"},{"pid":"d2657b2f81721c20d7828f18bcb97992bd36700a","tid":796382,"uid":3180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"受唔起，管理費已經交唔起<br />\n交埋差餉<br />\n<br />\n如果本身頭家呢啲費用、水電煤都係個女仔交<br />\n仲有家用<br />\n<br />\n咁佢可能真係唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993c83d13c2354604e63b0d59a62ec83125cdab9","tid":796382,"uid":99048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"唔通答你：好呀，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1fb51613be3549212bc482bcfb9c3b7fc46e88","tid":796382,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"夠晒上進心"},{"pid":"dcba57b00bcff1fe2c9099b033ad5ac1eaf514c2","tid":796382,"uid":40065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"幫人交埋管理費啦懵撚"},{"pid":"eaf6bb85bcb4fe11b36e48863f846de5b21dc1db","tid":796382,"uid":185306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcba57b00bcff1fe2c9099b033ad5ac1eaf514c2","tid":796382,"uid":40065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"幫人交埋管理費啦懵撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"又唔係我條我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我舉例咋喎"},{"pid":"6e18c985e7e939c62820530245d4cc318ade8dc4","tid":796382,"uid":185306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo